<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA30">
<l>iṅkillai paṇṭupōl vīṟṟirutta leṉṉuṭaiya</l>
<l>ceṅkaṇmāl cīrkkuñ ciṟituḷḷa maṅkē</l>
<l>maṭiyaṭakki niṟpataṉil valviṉaiyār tāmīṇ</l>
<l>ṭaṭiyeṭuppa taṉṟō vaḻaku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Here there is no sitting in disctinction, like formerly.</l>
<l>The mind is small even for the excellence of my red-eyed Māl. There,</l>
<l>without restraining [their] cloth [and] staying [my] harsh deeds further</l>
<l>lifting [their] feet, is it not beauty?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
